==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: yŏu yī dā méi yī dā
===Etymology===
From the [[w:Dream of the Red Chamber|Dream of the Red Chamber]]
===Idiom===
'''[[有]][[一]][[搭]][[沒]][[一]][[搭]]'''
# think of something to say without paying much heed to what one is saying.
===Alternate forms===
